654
01:15:11,449 --> 01:15:14,168
Ona je prva koja ce biti zrtvovana.

655
01:15:14,409 --> 01:15:17,765
Oslobodi me, Danny.
Prokletinje.

656
01:15:18,049 --> 01:15:19,926
Prvo joj odsecite jezik!

657
01:15:20,169 --> 01:15:26,439
Kada prestane sa bogohuljenjem,
izvadite joj srce!

658
01:15:26,810 --> 01:15:28,562
Prizovi se pameti, Danny.

659
01:15:28,810 --> 01:15:33,281
Njihova krv ce pomoci da izrastu
nove klice zivota.

660
01:15:33,730 --> 01:15:36,688
Neka nova zetva pocne!

661
01:15:39,330 --> 01:15:43,164
Mi smo jedno!

662
01:15:51,011 --> 01:15:53,206
Pogledaj me, Danny.

663
01:15:54,891 --> 01:15:56,688
Prestanite.

664
01:16:05,291 --> 01:16:07,965
Tamo u kukuruzu.
-On dolazi!

665
01:16:08,212 --> 01:16:10,851
Sada, Danny. On to zeli.

666
01:16:11,132 --> 01:16:14,363
Mi smo jedno!

667
01:16:22,772 --> 01:16:25,730
Danny, pomozi mi.
Preklinjem te.

668
01:16:38,333 --> 01:16:40,563
Gotovo je!

669
01:16:49,373 --> 01:16:52,046
Ubijte nevernike.

670
01:17:01,974 --> 01:17:04,124
Pazi!

671
01:17:05,214 --> 01:17:07,682
Bezi odatle!

672
01:17:13,694 --> 01:17:15,890
Ovamo, Frank.

673
01:17:30,215 --> 01:17:32,331
Hajde.

674
01:17:49,776 --> 01:17:55,328
Ubijte ih, ili cemo svi
ispastati od Onog Koji Hoda Iznad Ruza!

675
01:18:00,416 --> 01:18:02,453
Bezi!

676
01:18:07,737 --> 01:18:11,412
Sta se desava?
Trebalo je vec da nas stignu!

677
01:18:12,897 --> 01:18:15,286
Idemo ovuda!

678
01:18:35,858 --> 01:18:37,894
Stizu nas!

679
01:18:47,099 --> 01:18:50,171
Stani. Idemo u krug!

680
01:19:05,419 --> 01:19:07,853
Mrdaj!

681
01:19:08,740 --> 01:19:10,935
Stanite!

682
01:19:32,901 --> 01:19:38,259
Da li stvarno mislite da ce
Onaj Koji Hoda Iznad Ruza...

683
01:19:38,901 --> 01:19:42,974
vama dozvoliti da pobegnete?

684
01:19:51,861 --> 01:19:54,854
Razocarao si me, Danny.

685
01:19:55,782 --> 01:19:58,774
Sada te moramo tretirati kao i ostale!

686
01:19:59,022 --> 01:20:01,582
Zaustavi ovo sada, Micah.
-Tisina!

687
01:20:06,622 --> 01:20:08,817
Povuci se!

688
01:20:10,342 --> 01:20:15,496
Krv onih koji su se ogresili o
kukuruz mora poteci u zemlju!

689
01:20:16,623 --> 01:20:18,579
Na kolena!

690
01:20:21,143 --> 01:20:23,373
Na kolena!

691
01:21:05,225 --> 01:21:06,658
Bezimo!

692
01:21:06,905 --> 01:21:09,373
Pomozite mi!

693
01:21:09,705 --> 01:21:13,539
Molim te, Danny.
-Hajde, Danny.

694
01:21:13,785 --> 01:21:15,935
Molim te, Danny, ti si moj prijatelj!

695
01:21:16,185 --> 01:21:18,460
Vodi devojke, i bezi odavde, Danny.

696
01:21:24,146 --> 01:21:25,659
Ja sam bio uz tebe!

697
01:21:25,906 --> 01:21:27,578
Rekao sam: BEZI!

698
01:21:28,426 --> 01:21:30,542
Molim te, Danny, ti si moj prijatelj!

699
01:21:58,747 --> 01:22:01,136
Nastavite dalje!

700
01:22:26,868 --> 01:22:29,666
Ne, hajde! Hajde!

701
01:23:10,510 --> 01:23:13,980
Jesi li stvarno mislila to sto si rekla?

702
01:23:15,310 --> 01:23:18,109
Rekla bih bilo sta samo da me
spases iz tog pakla!

703
01:23:18,351 --> 01:23:21,024
Hocu da idem sa tobom u New York!

704
01:23:26,511 --> 01:23:28,741
Idemo, Danny.

705
01:23:48,192 --> 01:23:50,069
Sta ce se desiti sa decom?

706
01:23:50,912 --> 01:23:54,427
Ispricacemo njihovu pricu.
Da isceljenje pocne!

707
01:23:55,032 --> 01:23:57,148
Nije kasno za to?
-Ne.

708
01:24:02,833 --> 01:24:07,588
Mozda ce saradnik reportera u Newsweek
razmisliti o tome!

709
01:24:08,313 --> 01:24:11,669
Nije valjda da neko prodje kroz
sve ovo samo zbog price?

710
01:24:15,793 --> 01:24:17,749
Dobar si tata!

711
01:24:32,474 --> 01:24:35,466
Oznacava da je duh
bio jedno sa kukuruzom...

712
01:24:35,714 --> 01:24:39,548
i oslobadja se u onom ko nadje
istinu u sebi!

